01:38:40.200 --> 01:38:42.202
There are things more
pathetic than that.

01:38:42.520 --> 01:38:43.601
Yeah, like?

01:38:43.680 --> 01:38:45.011
- That moustache.
- (BOTH LAUGHING)

01:38:50.360 --> 01:38:52.328
ANNIE OVER SPEAKER:
<i>Riggan, we are in the motel.</i>

01:38:52.400 --> 01:38:55.370
<i>Last scene has started.
You're not here.</i>

01:38:55.680 --> 01:38:57.682
<i>Last chance for "places."</i>

01:38:58.240 --> 01:39:00.208
You better get back to your seat.

01:39:08.360 --> 01:39:09.361
(DOOR OPENS)

01:39:12.000 --> 01:39:13.001
(DOOR CLOSES)

